headline: CME Group, FanDuel Partner on New Stock, Commodity Bets
summary: Lynne Fitzpatrick, CME Group President and CFO, says the partnership with FanDuel is about distribution to customers, with FanDuel seeking additional access to financial market products. She tells Romaine Bostick and Scarlet Fu on "The Close" that FanDuel will bring millions of potential customers.
